ent-RMCMatebaCustomizationCaseLuxury-name = luxurious mateba customization kit case
ent-RMCMatebaCustomizationCaseLuxury-desc = A black case used for storing the tools and parts needed to customize a Mateba revolver. This variant is made for general-grade golden Matebas and comes with golden barrel attachments

